{"tid":2143291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專訪白頭佬：我無做錯！","createTime":"2020-08-07T04:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T04:51:07.000Z","uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"019974e0ed3cf2a233397d78a9fad914c1117058","tid":2143291,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"不覺選主席離場有錯 稱梁君彥必當選<br />\n<br />\n建制人數佔優成梁耀忠感「做唔到嘢」的原因，他以4年前今屆任期之初他主持立法會主席選舉為例，不少人罵他離場、令現任主席梁君彥當選，<span class=\"red\">「不是我令他選到，知不知道，怎樣選他也能當選」</span>。他說，建制派人數多造就梁君彥必然當選。他至今不覺自己當日有錯，強調無機制容許他審查主席候選人持雙重國籍，反問如不贊成考會考、文憑試，「是否可以撼爛制度？」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200806/s00002/1596651863778/議會生涯25年-懷緬以往「成功爭取」-梁耀忠無奈今屆做唔到嘢\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200806%2Fs00002%2F1596651863778%2F%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%AF25%E5%B9%B4-%E6%87%B7%E7%B7%AC%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80%E3%80%8C%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E3%80%8D-%E6%A2%81%E8%80%80%E5%BF%A0%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E4%BB%8A%E5%B1%86%E5%81%9A%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%98%A2&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=9dd81253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200806%2Fs00002%2F1596651863778%2F%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%AF25%E5%B9%B4-%E6%87%B7%E7%B7%AC%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80%E3%80%8C%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E3%80%8D-%E6%A2%81%E8%80%80%E5%BF%A0%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E4%BB%8A%E5%B1%86%E5%81%9A%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%98%A2&h=943b87ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200806/s00002/1596651863778/議會生涯25年-懷緬以往「成功爭取」-梁耀忠無奈今屆做唔到嘢</a>"},{"pid":"8ff63eb0c18745f10dc69397df734d350f4977dd","tid":2143291,"uid":104760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s